title: Narrative

* This example shows a simple table of contents with the ''toc-itemTemplate'' field

* The "root" elements are ''tagged Contents''

* Tiddler `aa-aa` has a `toc-itemTemplate` field pointing to `my-node-template`

* This overrides the default template for that ''specific node only''

* The macro is called ''without'' the itemTemplate parameter

{{examples-overview}}

+
title: Description

Field "toc-itemTemplate" overrides template per node
+
title: my-node-template

<$checkbox tag="done"/> - <<_linkTemplate>>

+
title: aa-aa
tags: aa
toc-itemTemplate: my-node-template

Link to [[bb]]

